text: Peter Sainthill may refer to: * Peter Sainthill (died 1571) (1524-1571), Member Parliament for Grampound * Peter Sainthill (1593-1648), Member of Parliament for Tiverton in Devon * Peter Sainthill (surgeon) (1698-1775), British 18th century surgeon and a Fellow of the Royal Society
title: Peter Sainthill (disambiguation)
